svg.title: what-i-do
svg.text: My brain is constantly flowing with ideas due to my interestand experience in the different fields. Design keeps my brain active and my creativity allows me to generate, develop, and communicate new ideas.

Every design for me starts on paper. Paper prototyping and wire framing are technique that allows me to create and test ideas quickly and cheaply. It's easier to change a prototype than the final design.
Throughout university I have developed experience in designing and building websites for many different purposes. I have gained an understanding of HTML and CSS to create engaging experiences.
Vector Illustration is one of my main passions. I enjoy the ability to combine art and design to create lively illustrations that convey a subjective mood, personality and character.
